1
00:00:27,416 --> 00:00:28,458
Yes, I did it.

2
00:00:28,625 --> 00:00:29,583
I don't want to talk about this anymore.

3
00:00:30,125 --> 00:00:32,000
You're always like this, Nok.

4
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:34,708
I don't understand
how you can't feel anything.

5
00:00:40,583 --> 00:00:41,916
I want to know how you feel.

6
00:00:42,791 --> 00:00:44,458
We're getting married, Nok.

7
00:00:44,625 --> 00:00:45,708
You can talk to me.

8
00:00:46,416 --> 00:00:47,708
Okay. If that's what you want.

9
00:00:48,166 --> 00:00:49,583
Thana! Watch out!

10
00:02:29,833 --> 00:02:33,958
Hey, did you go jogging this morning?
I thought I saw you.

11
00:02:35,583 --> 00:02:36,583
Yes.

12
00:02:38,333 --> 00:02:39,958
I like to go running.

13
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:43,625
To prepare myself for the big test.

14
00:02:44,541 --> 00:02:46,916
The big test.

15
00:02:47,875 --> 00:02:50,208
You're going to meet that guy today.

16
00:02:51,375 --> 00:02:52,583
Be careful.

17
00:02:54,166 --> 00:02:55,291
All right.

18
00:02:55,708 --> 00:02:57,666
I heard he was talented
but not so friendly.

19
00:03:00,250 --> 00:03:02,000
It's getting worse, Doctor.

20
00:03:02,625 --> 00:03:04,833
This doesn't help.
Blood pressure is not increasing.

21
00:03:08,041 --> 00:03:10,416
BP is dropping to 80/40.

22
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,916
Doctor, shall we prepare blood
for a transfusion?

23
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,833
