-Yes, Doctor.

24
00:03:15,958 --> 00:03:19,000
Blood pressure is decreasing.
The dosage we gave is not sustaining.

25
00:03:19,166 --> 00:03:21,541
I'm aware of that. I'm trying.
Apply suction here, please.

26
00:03:22,916 --> 00:03:25,333
