DR. KARN
DR. PANTHANA

102
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,333
You're interested in this story, right?

103
00:08:11,458 --> 00:08:13,916
There's more to it.

104
00:08:14,083 --> 00:08:17,458
Dr. Thana has remained single ever since.

105
00:08:19,166 --> 00:08:22,125
If he's that handsome and that great,

106
00:08:22,208 --> 00:08:25,083
how come nobody
has offered to heal his wound?

107
00:08:26,375 --> 00:08:31,583
There were some,
but he wasn't really interested.

108
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:36,083
And some of them encountered some mishaps.

109
00:08:40,125 --> 00:08:41,083
Mishaps?

110
00:08:43,708 --> 00:08:45,000
The ghost of Dr. Nok.

111
00:08:47,250 --> 00:08:48,583
They say that

112
00:08:49,583 --> 00:08:51,166
those young nurses

113
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:54,000
who hit on Dr. Thana
met with some unfortunate events.

114
00:09:01,416 --> 00:09:02,875
Tenth floor, door opening.

115
00:09:08,166 --> 00:09:09,958
He's cute.

116
00:09:10,041 --> 00:09:11,625
Door closing.

117
00:09:11,708 --> 00:09:15,000
I've been here a long time.
I don't even dare to give him my number.

118
00:09:15,083 --> 00:09:16,625
That's crazy.

119
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,750
Thirteenth floor, door opening.

120
00:09:27,375 --> 00:09:28,833
Why don't you come out?

121
00:10:00,625 --> 00:10:02,666
-Is that true?
-I don't know if it's true or not.

122
00:10:02,875 --> 00:10:04,958
I've never tried to hit on Dr. Thana.

123
00:10:05,916 --> 00:10:07,583
Or do you want to give it a go?

124
00:10:15,583 --> 00:10:17,750
I'm going.

125
00:10:17,875 --> 00:10:19,166
I'm scared.

126
00:10:34,333 --> 00:10:37,041
-Iced cappuccino, not too sweet.
-Here.

127
00:10:52,416 --> 00:10:54,083
Latte for Dr. Thana.

128
00:10:55,875 --> 00:10:57,583
Americano for Dr. Nok.

129
00:11:36,875 --> 00:11:39,500
I want to say sorry
and thank you for yesterday.

130
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,000
So do you want to apologize
or thank me first?

131
00:11:45,541 --> 00:11:46,916
Sorry first,

132
00:11:47,791 --> 00:11:49,791
for arguing with you.

133
00:11:50,625 --> 00:11:52,875
And thank you for your help
with the surgery.

134
00:11:59,416 --> 00:12:00,666
Please, sit down.

135
00:12:19,291 --> 00:12:21,750
I guess someone must have told you things.

136
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:34,875
What's your opinion, then?

137
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,458
You like to have
two different kinds of coffee.

138
00:12:42,875 --> 00:12:44,000
Nok and I...

139
00:12:48,708 --> 00:12:49,833
Nok and I...

140
00:12:51,291 --> 00:12:53,083
We liked different things.

141
00:12:54,333 --> 00:12:56,166
We would always argue...

142
00:12:57,208 --> 00:12:59,166
about whose coffee tasted better.

143
00:13:02,416 --> 00:13:04,500
Try my Americano.

144
00:13:05,291 --> 00:13:07,666
No, Nok. I think it's bitter.

145
00:13:08,833 --> 00:13:10,166
Come on, try it.

146
00:13:10,708 --> 00:13:12,166
Bitterness is good.

147
00:13:25,833 --> 00:13:27,208
The latte is not bad.

148
00:13:27,708 --> 00:13:30,041
The level of sweetness is just right.

149
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:34,083
And your Americano is weirdly bitter.

150
00:14:01,166 --> 00:14:03,125
We drank half of each other's cups.

151
00:14:04,625 --> 00:14:07,333
So I've been drinking
two types of coffee ever since.

152
00:14:11,333 --> 00:14:13,500
It's a clever way to solve an argument.

153
00:14:16,833 --> 00:14:18,166
If it's a clever way,

154
00:14:18,708 --> 00:14:20,958
then you're clever
for answering correctly.

155
00:14:21,708 --> 00:14:23,000
You're the first.

156
00:14:31,041 --> 00:14:33,708
Other people think I order it for Nok.

157
00:14:45,625 --> 00:14:47,250
Somebody needs me.

158
00:14:55,875 --> 00:15:00,541
The two kinds of coffee thing
is a secret I had never told anyone.

159
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:02,583
I've only told you.

160
00:15:04,583 --> 00:15:05,833
Keep it to yourself.

161
00:15:06,208 --> 00:15:08,375
Let people think whatever they want.

162
00:16:19,666 --> 00:16:20,708
How are you doing?

163
00:16:20,791 --> 00:16:22,250
-Hello.
-Hi.

164
00:16:22,791 --> 00:16:24,916
I don't know, the pain comes and goes.

165
00:16:26,291 --> 00:16:28,291
Let me look at your stomach.

166
00:16:35,416 --> 00:16:37,000
Have you been passing wind?

167
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:42,375
Farting. She wants to know
if you've been farting.

168
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,375
