but now I see that it's true.

172
00:17:07,583 --> 00:17:08,750
Thank you.

173
00:17:09,291 --> 00:17:11,666
She's not just pretty,
she's a great surgeon, too.

174
00:17:11,916 --> 00:17:13,416
Dr. Thana has been praising her.

175
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:14,875
The surgery was performed very well.

176
00:17:14,958 --> 00:17:16,541
