Dr. Thana is very good-looking.

179
00:17:20,125 --> 00:17:22,208
Is this a hospital or a catwalk?

180
00:17:22,666 --> 00:17:24,666
Hurry up and get well soon.
I'm getting jealous.

181
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:29,583
But Dr. Thana is not just handsome,
he's also romantic.

182
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,000
