183
00:17:32,208 --> 00:17:33,625
He's still single.

184
00:17:33,750 --> 00:17:35,958
I want to meet a nice guy like that.

185
00:17:36,125 --> 00:17:38,250
Fine, when you die, I'll do that for you.

186
00:17:39,458 --> 00:17:41,500
How come you know so much about this?

187
00:17:41,583 --> 00:17:43,500
All the nurses
have been gossiping about it.

188
00:17:44,041 --> 00:17:46,000
But his girlfriend must have been
so amazing.

189
00:17:46,166 --> 00:17:48,708
Otherwise, he would be over her already.

190
00:17:49,125 --> 00:17:51,041
Can you be as cool as her?

191
00:17:51,833 --> 00:17:53,000
Asshole!

192
00:17:55,541 --> 00:17:56,875
Dr. Bee.

193
00:17:57,166 --> 00:17:58,708
Don't you want to have a boyfriend?

194
00:17:58,791 --> 00:18:01,541
You're pretty
and Dr. Thana is good-looking.

195
00:18:02,291 --> 00:18:03,750
You would be great together.

196
00:18:05,875 --> 00:18:07,500
Get plenty of rest, okay?

197
00:18:10,083 --> 00:18:13,750
Don't encourage that.
The ghost of Dr. Nok will come for you.

198
00:18:14,375 --> 00:18:17,250
You bastard, don't joke like that!
I'm already scared.

199
00:18:25,708 --> 00:18:26,958
Yes, June?

200
00:18:27,875 --> 00:18:31,208
Don't forget about
the new residents party tonight.

201
00:18:31,625 --> 00:18:33,625
I heard that person will be there too.

202
00:18:37,041 --> 00:18:38,208
