212
00:21:23,458 --> 00:21:26,416
That's Tree,
she's a pharmaceutical representative.

213
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:29,125
Her parents own a private hospital.

214
00:21:29,208 --> 00:21:30,583
Her family is really rich.

215
00:21:32,041 --> 00:21:33,583
It's good to be Dr. Thana.

216
00:21:33,916 --> 00:21:36,500
The harder he is to get,
the more women want him.

217
00:22:30,583 --> 00:22:31,833
What are you laughing at?

218
00:22:33,625 --> 00:22:36,500
I want to thank that new doctor.

219
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:39,958
Thanks to her, you gave in to me.

220
00:22:41,208 --> 00:22:42,750
This time, you even brought me back home.

221
00:22:43,958 --> 00:22:45,666
What does she have to do with it?

222
00:22:46,250 --> 00:22:47,541
Come on.

223
00:22:48,083 --> 00:22:49,500
I saw you looking at her.

224
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:55,416
I was thinking about the time
when Nok and I were new residents.

225
00:22:55,666 --> 00:22:56,791
I miss Nok.

226
00:22:57,583 --> 00:23:00,666
It's so convenient to be a guy.

227
00:23:02,041 --> 00:23:03,916
You miss you one woman,

228
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,708
but you bring another one home.

229
00:23:19,083 --> 00:23:20,208
I'll be back.

230
00:24:16,791 --> 00:24:18,000
So beautiful.

231
00:24:25,625 --> 00:24:27,541
You can stay and watch if you like.

232
00:26:15,083 --> 00:26:16,208
Thana!

233
00:26:18,541 --> 00:26:19,583
Thana!

234
00:26:21,333 --> 00:26:22,333
Thana!

235
00:26:25,500 --> 00:26:26,666
Thana!

236
00:26:28,208 --> 00:26:29,250
Thana!

237
00:26:31,833 --> 00:26:32,958
Thana!

238
00:26:33,500 --> 00:26:34,625
Thana!

239
00:26:38,625 --> 00:26:39,625
Thana!

240
00:27:22,750 --> 00:27:24,333
Did you have a rough night?

241
00:27:30,125 --> 00:27:31,458
Not really.

242
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:35,166
In the end, it wasn't like
how people think it was.

243
00:27:36,791 --> 00:27:38,791
Only the beginning was unbelievable.

244
00:27:40,333 --> 00:27:41,291
Why is that?

245
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:45,375
The beginning was very normal.

246
00:27:46,416 --> 00:27:47,500
Women...

247
00:27:49,958 --> 00:27:52,125
They come and go as they please.

248
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:56,750
And men...

249
00:27:57,458 --> 00:28:01,000
They ask you to come when they want you.
If not, they tell you to go away.

250
00:28:01,500 --> 00:28:04,250
She was okay about it and so was I,
so it was fine.

251
00:28:06,125 --> 00:28:07,375
Or did you think...

252
00:28:10,625 --> 00:28:11,708
What did I think?

253
00:28:14,125 --> 00:28:15,083
Dr. Bee.

254
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:19,291
Do you need to love someone
to have sex with them?

255
00:28:53,166 --> 00:28:54,291
Hi, Bee.

256
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:55,833
About before...

257
00:28:56,625 --> 00:28:58,500
I want to apologize and thank you.

258
00:29:00,625 --> 00:29:01,708
