259
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,375
Sorry for...

260
00:29:03,916 --> 00:29:05,125
being rude to you.

261
00:29:05,500 --> 00:29:07,666
I was annoyed with myself.

262
00:29:08,250 --> 00:29:09,875
