263
00:29:11,166 --> 00:29:12,583
For forgiving me.

264
00:29:15,125 --> 00:29:18,000
I never thought you'd be the type
to say things like this.

265
00:29:18,083 --> 00:29:20,333
Get in, I'll take you home.

