646
01:24:44,833 --> 01:24:48,083
The number you have dialed
is not available at this time.

647
01:25:43,250 --> 01:25:44,916
SEAMSTRESS FOR HIRE

648
01:25:51,458 --> 01:25:54,416
The number you are calling
is not available.

649
01:25:54,833 --> 01:25:56,791
Please try again later.

650
01:26:04,583 --> 01:26:05,833
What is it, Mom?

651
01:26:06,208 --> 01:26:07,458
A woman called.

652
01:26:08,666 --> 01:26:12,000
She told me to warn you
to stop fooling around with her husband.

653
01:26:14,958 --> 01:26:16,875
-Who--
-Why didn't you listen to me?

654
01:26:22,416 --> 01:26:24,250
Did she tell you her name?

655
01:26:25,750 --> 01:26:27,333
She said her name was Nok.

656
01:26:47,250 --> 01:26:48,416
Thana.

657
01:26:50,375 --> 01:26:51,416
Thana.

658
01:26:54,458 --> 01:26:55,541
Thana.

659
01:26:59,666 --> 01:27:00,791
Thana.

660
01:27:05,791 --> 01:27:07,041
Thana.

661
01:27:14,791 --> 01:27:16,250
Nok.

662
01:30:19,333 --> 01:30:20,375
Is this you?

663
01:30:21,333 --> 01:30:22,541
Yes, it's me.

664
01:30:24,750 --> 01:30:26,166
That's all I wanted to know.

665
01:30:27,291 --> 01:30:29,125
I didn't think she would do that.

666
01:30:30,208 --> 01:30:31,708
It's not what she did.

667
01:30:35,875 --> 01:30:37,083
Yes, I did it.

668
01:30:42,583 --> 01:30:44,708
And do you want to know why I did it?

669
01:30:46,541 --> 01:30:48,041
I don't want to talk about this.

670
01:30:48,291 --> 01:30:49,791
You're always like this, Nok.

671
01:30:50,625 --> 01:30:52,125
We have to talk about it.

672
01:30:52,708 --> 01:30:54,250
We're about to get married.

673
01:31:00,375 --> 01:31:01,583
You don't understand.

674
01:31:01,958 --> 01:31:03,666
Yeah, I don't understand.

675
01:31:05,166 --> 01:31:07,541
I don't understand
how you can't feel anything.

676
01:31:09,875 --> 01:31:11,583
You think I'm tired of you.

677
01:31:12,250 --> 01:31:13,708
Or I love you less?

678
01:31:27,458 --> 01:31:29,916
All right, if you want to hear it.

679
01:31:34,041 --> 01:31:36,541
Our love has never changed.

680
01:31:39,541 --> 01:31:42,541
I believe that even
though you slept with her,

681
01:31:42,625 --> 01:31:44,708
you still love me just the same.

682
01:31:46,083 --> 01:31:48,916
But what's changing is...

683
01:31:49,000 --> 01:31:50,291
Thana, watch out!

684
01:33:04,166 --> 01:33:05,416
How are you?

685
01:33:14,083 --> 01:33:15,375
How did I get here?

686
01:33:16,416 --> 01:33:18,083
You passed out in the car.

687
01:33:21,916 --> 01:33:23,208
Last night...

688
01:33:25,875 --> 01:33:26,958
Dr. Nok, right?

689
01:33:31,291 --> 01:33:32,875
I saw that photo.

690
01:33:33,541 --> 01:33:34,541
What photo?

691
01:33:50,625 --> 01:33:51,625
Yes.

692
01:33:52,250 --> 01:33:54,875
I was wrong. I cheated on her.

693
01:33:56,375 --> 01:33:58,791
She was still mad at me, so she did this.

694
01:34:00,416 --> 01:34:01,625
Why do you think so?

695
01:34:06,625 --> 01:34:10,250
At first, I thought
Nok would have accepted you.

696
01:34:12,166 --> 01:34:14,000
Because you and her are alike somehow...

697
01:34:17,250 --> 01:34:19,833
but she refused to give in.

698
01:34:22,500 --> 01:34:25,166
She didn't want me to start over
with someone else.

699
01:34:29,375 --> 01:34:31,208
That's all you cared about?

700
01:34:33,958 --> 01:34:35,333
You slept with me...

701
01:34:37,250 --> 01:34:39,875
because I'm similar to Nok, right?

702
01:34:45,458 --> 01:34:46,625
You should go home.

703
01:35:56,208 --> 01:35:57,416
Well, here we go again.

704
01:35:58,250 --> 01:35:59,083
Please, come in.

705
01:36:03,250 --> 01:36:04,333
You go first.

706
01:36:20,875 --> 01:36:22,166
What is it?

707
01:36:22,833 --> 01:36:24,208
You're so evil.

708
01:36:26,083 --> 01:36:31,166
Did you know this picture
made them argue and led to the accident?

709
01:36:33,791 --> 01:36:35,375
Let me tell you something.

710
01:36:36,208 --> 01:36:38,041
Do you know why men cheat?

711
01:36:38,666 --> 01:36:42,625
Because sometimes,
they get bored of good girls,

712
01:36:42,958 --> 01:36:45,458
well-mannered like princesses.

713
01:36:46,375 --> 01:36:50,208
So if there is a hero and a princess,
there must be a villain.

714
01:36:50,958 --> 01:36:52,958
You should thank me, instead,

715
01:36:53,041 --> 01:36:57,166
for helping to prove
the true love between Thana and Nok.

716
01:36:58,458 --> 01:36:59,500
Just like you.

717
01:37:02,625 --> 01:37:03,875
How?

718
01:37:05,750 --> 01:37:07,625
You've already slept with him, right?

719
01:37:13,416 --> 01:37:16,875
Normally, when people fight
over something,

720
01:37:17,166 --> 01:37:20,583
they always bring out their good sides
to bluff other people.

721
01:37:21,041 --> 01:37:22,791
Some are good at understanding.

722
01:37:23,458 --> 01:37:25,333
Some are good at caring.

723
01:37:27,791 --> 01:37:29,583
And some are good in bed.

724
01:37:32,083 --> 01:37:36,458
If fighting over something is so bad,
then we three are bad people.

725
01:37:38,291 --> 01:37:40,250
As for Nok,

726
01:37:40,375 --> 01:37:44,333
when she knew that Thana cheated on her,
she took the easy way out and died.

727
01:37:45,333 --> 01:37:47,250
So Thana's heart will forever be with her.

728
01:37:48,416 --> 01:37:49,500
That was so bad.

729
01:37:51,041 --> 01:37:52,458
Nok was not like that.

730
01:37:53,833 --> 01:37:55,458
Oh, God!

731
01:37:56,500 --> 01:37:58,291
You're so naive.

732
01:37:59,541 --> 01:38:02,083
Or you're just pretending to be...

733
01:38:03,208 --> 01:38:08,666
I know you're listening to us.

734
01:38:09,125 --> 01:38:12,875
You're probably laughing at us
for fighting over something we can't have.

735
01:38:15,375 --> 01:38:16,541
What?

736
01:38:17,625 --> 01:38:18,875
You think I'm crazy?

737
01:38:19,916 --> 01:38:22,500
Don't tell me you haven't seen
the ghost of Nok?

738
01:38:28,583 --> 01:38:30,791
There. I told you.

739
01:38:31,083 --> 01:38:33,291
She is so possessive.

740
01:38:42,000 --> 01:38:43,625
One more thing...

741
01:38:45,375 --> 01:38:47,791
ghosts can't make phone calls.

742
01:38:52,916 --> 01:38:54,458
The person who called your mom

743
01:38:56,125 --> 01:38:57,291
was me.

744
01:39:00,833 --> 01:39:03,000
Consider it as my welcome present.

745
01:39:05,458 --> 01:39:07,750
My mom has nothing to do with this.

746
01:39:27,333 --> 01:39:28,708
THANA

747
01:39:33,666 --> 01:39:39,083
The number you are calling
is not available.

748
01:39:51,958 --> 01:39:54,791
You still remember where my place is.

749
01:39:57,250 --> 01:39:58,750
I thought you had forgotten about it.

750
01:40:01,958 --> 01:40:04,708
You're in such a rush.

751
01:40:06,791 --> 01:40:08,000
Finally,

752
01:40:09,000 --> 01:40:10,708
you've come back to your done deal.

753
01:40:11,416 --> 01:40:13,875
A done deal is great.

754
01:40:14,666 --> 01:40:16,250
There's no fuss.

755
01:40:16,625 --> 01:40:18,375
There's no running away.

756
01:40:21,291 --> 01:40:22,833
Nok!

757
01:40:28,791 --> 01:40:29,958
You!

758
01:40:31,833 --> 01:40:33,291
I didn't do it!

759
01:40:35,333 --> 01:40:36,916
It was an accident.

760
01:40:38,291 --> 01:40:40,250
Don't make me feel guilty!

761
01:40:40,875 --> 01:40:42,041
It wasn't my fault!

762
01:40:42,958 --> 01:40:45,000
Don't come any closer!

763
01:40:45,083 --> 01:40:46,875
I didn't know! I didn't do it!

764
01:40:47,041 --> 01:40:48,666
It was an accident!

765
01:40:49,166 --> 01:40:51,250
It's not my fault!

766
01:41:34,958 --> 01:41:36,250
I've always thought

767
01:41:37,666 --> 01:41:39,708
that the love between you and Thana

768
01:41:41,875 --> 01:41:43,833
is such a beautiful thing.

769
01:41:44,916 --> 01:41:46,250
But in reality,

770
01:41:46,958 --> 01:41:49,125
love is terrible, isn't it?

771
01:41:50,208 --> 01:41:52,416
No matter how good we are...

772
01:41:55,250 --> 01:41:56,958
in the end,

773
01:41:58,000 --> 01:42:01,583
we have to be evil when someone tries
to take something that we love.

774
01:42:10,833 --> 01:42:11,875
Then, go ahead...

775
01:42:16,083 --> 01:42:17,958
I'm right here right now.

776
01:42:20,916 --> 01:42:22,541
Do what you have to do.

777
01:42:24,166 --> 01:42:26,708
If you think I'm taking Thana
away from you...

778
01:42:29,416 --> 01:42:30,750
do it, Dr. Nok.

779
