get the defib ready.

788
01:46:52,541 --> 01:46:54,333
Where's Dr. Varaporn?

789
01:47:09,208 --> 01:47:10,625
Calm down.

790
01:47:11,833 --> 01:47:13,166
Everything is going to be okay.

791
01:47:14,625 --> 01:47:17,458
Many things are not what they seem to be,

792
01:47:17,541 --> 01:47:18,791
Doctor.

793
01:48:00,875 --> 01:48:02,541
You're thinking about Nok, aren't you?

794
01:48:14,375 --> 01:48:16,291
I'm thinking about you, too.

795
01:48:19,166 --> 01:48:20,250
Nok.

796
01:48:23,583 --> 01:48:24,791
I miss you.

797
01:48:30,500 --> 01:48:32,166
I'm on my way to be with you.

798
01:48:37,541 --> 01:48:38,916
Like I said...

799
01:48:42,916 --> 01:48:44,250
Wherever you go,

800
01:48:46,250 --> 01:48:47,541
I'll follow you.

801
01:48:50,500 --> 01:48:51,708
I know.

802
01:48:53,208 --> 01:48:55,541
-We're bound together.
-We're bound together.

803
01:48:56,583 --> 01:48:57,791
Wherever you go,

804
01:48:57,875 --> 01:48:59,375
-I'll follow you.
-I'll follow you.

805
01:49:00,041 --> 01:49:02,291
When you're happy,

806
01:49:04,125 --> 01:49:05,708
I'll be in front of you.

807
01:49:06,791 --> 01:49:08,625
When you're down,

808
01:49:09,583 --> 01:49:11,208
I'll be next to you.

809
01:49:13,458 --> 01:49:14,875
When you're sad,

810
01:49:16,791 --> 01:49:18,166
I'll be right behind you.

811
01:49:18,833 --> 01:49:19,875
Yes.

812
01:49:23,666 --> 01:49:25,458
But you can't come with me.

813
01:49:28,708 --> 01:49:30,166
I have to go.

814
01:49:31,833 --> 01:49:34,833
But you have to live on.

815
01:49:40,875 --> 01:49:43,541
I want you to live on with this woman.

816
01:49:45,583 --> 01:49:47,083
Or anyone.

817
01:49:48,750 --> 01:49:50,333
As long as you are happy.

818
01:49:55,208 --> 01:49:56,750
But why...

819
01:49:59,125 --> 01:50:00,958
Why are you still around me?

820
01:50:03,916 --> 01:50:06,083
You're still close to me

821
01:50:06,166 --> 01:50:07,625
all the time.

822
01:50:16,500 --> 01:50:18,791
Think carefully about it, Thana.

823
01:50:19,833 --> 01:50:21,208
Why...

824
01:50:21,791 --> 01:50:23,750
Why I'm still around you.

825
01:50:25,458 --> 01:50:28,083
Why I'm still lingering,

826
01:50:28,166 --> 01:50:29,333
never leaving.

827
01:50:39,041 --> 01:50:41,583
Nok, no.

828
01:50:45,041 --> 01:50:46,333
Nok, don't go.

829
01:50:46,500 --> 01:50:48,125
Come back, Nok.

830
01:50:48,208 --> 01:50:51,375
Come back, Nok.
Wherever you go, I'll follow.

831
01:51:04,416 --> 01:51:06,666
We drank half of each other's cup.

832
01:51:07,833 --> 01:51:10,916
So I've been drinking
two types of coffee ever since.

833
01:51:15,958 --> 01:51:17,500
For the last two years,

834
01:51:18,916 --> 01:51:20,541
I visit this place once a year.

835
01:51:25,333 --> 01:51:26,541
Now this binds us together.

836
01:51:27,875 --> 01:51:30,125
Wherever you go,

837
01:51:30,208 --> 01:51:31,500
I'll follow.

838
01:51:34,666 --> 01:51:37,291
It looks like it's not just binding.
We're going to be stuck together.

839
01:51:46,458 --> 01:51:47,583
Because of me?

840
01:51:50,208 --> 01:51:51,416
Because of you.

841
01:51:54,750 --> 01:51:55,833
You miss me.

842
01:51:59,500 --> 01:52:00,958
You won't let go.

843
01:52:22,708 --> 01:52:24,333
I've been trying to tell you,

844
01:52:25,375 --> 01:52:27,083
but you just can't see it.

845
01:52:29,333 --> 01:52:30,875
You can't feel it.

846
01:52:46,166 --> 01:52:47,625
I'm sorry.

847
01:52:53,375 --> 01:52:54,833
I'm sorry.

848
01:52:56,041 --> 01:52:57,750
You don't have to be sorry,

849
01:52:59,333 --> 01:53:00,500
you did your best.

850
01:53:02,250 --> 01:53:04,000
You took the greatest care of me.

851
01:53:06,458 --> 01:53:07,791
I never thought

852
01:53:09,333 --> 01:53:11,125
that the love I have for you...

853
01:53:13,250 --> 01:53:14,708
had caused you pain.

854
01:53:15,708 --> 01:53:17,208
Love makes us happy.

855
01:53:18,958 --> 01:53:21,083
But we suffer because we miss each other.

856
01:53:22,208 --> 01:53:24,208
We love each other just the same.

857
01:53:24,416 --> 01:53:26,083
But we won't miss each other just as much.

858
01:53:26,791 --> 01:53:29,041
We'll care for each other less.

859
01:53:39,333 --> 01:53:40,666
I love you.

860
01:54:10,000 --> 01:54:11,958
We did everything we could.

861
01:54:13,750 --> 01:54:16,291
It's up to him now
when he will regain consciousness.

862
01:54:19,250 --> 01:54:20,708
Don't give up hope.

863
01:55:38,916 --> 01:55:40,125
Thana.

864
01:55:46,541 --> 01:55:47,625
I think...

865
01:55:48,958 --> 01:55:50,166
You have to choose.

866
01:55:51,416 --> 01:55:53,708
Which one of us do you want to make happy?

867
01:55:57,583 --> 01:55:58,583
Nok?

868
01:56:04,250 --> 01:56:05,416
Or me?

869
01:56:10,333 --> 01:56:11,583
If you don't wake up...

870
01:56:15,083 --> 01:56:17,000
then Nok will be very happy.

871
01:56:21,666 --> 01:56:22,583
But...

872
01:56:28,541 --> 01:56:30,000
I will miss you.

873
01:56:39,166 --> 01:56:41,291
I can never let you go.

874
01:56:47,833 --> 01:56:48,916
It's true that...

875
01:56:51,791 --> 01:56:55,750
I once told you
that I would step aside...

876
01:57:02,875 --> 01:57:04,333
if you were alive.

877
01:57:08,583 --> 01:57:09,916
But right now,

878
01:57:10,958 --> 01:57:12,458
I'll never give up.

879
01:57:19,666 --> 01:57:21,166
Wake up, Thana.

880
01:57:24,041 --> 01:57:25,333
Wake up and be with me.

881
01:57:28,166 --> 01:57:29,458
You have to wake up.

882
01:57:33,000 --> 01:57:34,291
Because I...

883
01:57:35,625 --> 01:57:37,375
can never lose you to someone else.

884
01:58:34,083 --> 01:58:35,791
I can no longer take it.

885
01:58:36,458 --> 01:58:41,083
I'm not letting you go.
You have to stay with me for a long time.

886
01:58:51,208 --> 01:58:53,541
-How is he, Doctor?
-The patient is not likely to make it.

887
01:58:53,625 --> 01:58:56,416
So, please, be prepared for the worst.

888
01:58:58,416 --> 01:59:00,041
You have to help our father!

889
01:59:00,125 --> 01:59:01,625
Don't let him die.

890
01:59:01,875 --> 01:59:03,583
You have to help him, Doctor.

891
01:59:03,666 --> 01:59:05,708
We did our best.

892
01:59:07,250 --> 01:59:08,958
Please, help.

893
01:59:20,750 --> 01:59:22,125
You're going to be all right.

894
01:59:22,208 --> 01:59:23,458
Please, stay with me.

895
01:59:24,333 --> 01:59:25,958
I'll be with you always.

